rows.label: tlk006301_09_msg0001
rows.name:
Luxuria has come out of the attack
relatively unscathed, perhaps due to
our proximity with the World Tree.

rows.label: tlk006301_09_msg0002
rows.name:
But I witnessed many Divine Beasts falling
into the Cloud Sea from afar...

rows.label: tlk006301_09_msg0003
rows.name: It seems Alst's final hour is at hand...

rows.label: tlk006301_09_msg0004
rows.name:
It pains me that Luxuria's decision
500 years ago would cause such
repercussions...
